{"tid":1740511,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真討論]有冇可能申請禁制令, 禁止使用催淚彈","createTime":"2019-11-20T03:06:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T13:57:00.000Z","uid":246697,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"74f824204139eaacb034911f2163413f1c699eb3","tid":1740511,"uid":246697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:06:38.000Z","msg":"而家用緊既大陸催淚彈毒到仆街就係人都知, 但我地有冇可能可以向法庭提出理據去禁止使用? 求法律JJ探討 / 解釋下<br />\n<br />\neg.<br />\n1. 明顯對自然環境有影響, eg.雀鳥大量死亡<br />\n2. 催淚彈已成常態, 成效已比運動初期大減, 示威者早已有大量措施應對催淚氣體<br />\n3. 香港街道狹窄, 容易波及無辜,  eg.老人院, 伊利沙伯醫院, 甚至誤射入民居之中<br />\n4. 未有指引去除殘餘催淚氣體物質<br />\n5. 已有個案因長期接觸催淚氣體引至不同疾病, 無論警方, 記者, 市民都會身受其害 eg.氯痤瘡<br />\n6. 當催淚氣體會造成其他未知影響/污染時唔應該繼續使用 eg. 二噁英<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手諗下"},{"pid":"1f1b34e8d5f3c483f522070d0c16e51163e2f72b","tid":1740511,"uid":169136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:07:53.000Z","msg":"要有多啲expert evidence先做到"},{"pid":"aea065f8d56c5e3f4395a5a587a45608f528d1c8","tid":1740511,"uid":246697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f1b34e8d5f3c483f522070d0c16e51163e2f72b","tid":1740511,"uid":169136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:07:53.000Z","msg":"要有多啲expert evidence先做到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:16:55.000Z","msg":"咁有冇可香港有認可既化驗所做到呢, 甚至邀請外國專家, 不過可能衍生其他問題<br />\n1. 對方肯唔肯做<br />\n2. 金錢<br />\n3. 拎去驗又話非法管有彈藥<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30ada84542061e0f5d9297417e3530519ca7ae8","tid":1740511,"uid":246697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:20:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce878d4631bd5d623b26a3dae5315bf1d58e3e65","tid":1740511,"uid":8397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTim